<div class = "uk-padding" id = "natural_col" style = "display:none">
<h3>Plain green, brown</h3>

<p> A plain colour scheme with green leaves and brown branches made to look like a tree. All leaves are shown in the same way under this colour scheme and so are all branches. It's useful if you're looking for simple colour scheme e.g. for {{=A('screenshots using our screenshot tool', _href=URL('education','screenshot_launcher.html'))}}, that doesn't require any further explanation.  </p>

<center><img src= "{{=URL('static','images/Screenshots/Life_spiral_brown.jpg')}}" alt="" ></img></center>




</div>

<div class = "uk-padding" id = "AT_col" style = "display:none">
<h3>Ancestor's tale</h3>

<p>With a colour scheme to match the front cover of the Ancestor's Tale (2016) book by Richard Dawkins and Yan Wong.  The book uses graphics from OneZoom throughout to illustrate sections of the tree of life. All leaves are shown in the same colour under this scheme.  Pictured is how this colour scheme looks when you select 'Ancestor's Tale' as the page content in settings as well.</p>


<center><img src= "{{=URL('static','images/Screenshots/AT_view.png')}}" alt="" ></img></center>



</div>


<script>
// checking that the theme can be seen here
if ((typeof onezoom.controller.get_color_theme != "undefined")&&(typeof onezoom.controller.get_color_theme_CBF != "undefined"))
{
    let color_theme = onezoom.controller.get_color_theme();
    let color_theme_CBF = onezoom.controller.get_color_theme_CBF();

    if (color_theme == "IUCN") {
        document.getElementById("General_col").style.display = "none"
        if (color_theme_CBF) {
            document.getElementById("IUCN_CBF_col").style.display = "block"
        } else {
            document.getElementById("IUCN_col").style.display = "block"
        }
    } else if (color_theme == "popularity") {
        document.getElementById("General_col").style.display = "none"
        if (color_theme_CBF) {
            document.getElementById("popularity_CBF_col").style.display = "block"
        } else {
            document.getElementById("popularity_col").style.display = "block"
        }
    } else if (color_theme == "AT") {
        document.getElementById("General_col").style.display = "none"
        document.getElementById("AT_col").style.display = "block"
    } else if (color_theme == "natural") {
        document.getElementById("General_col").style.display = "none"
        document.getElementById("natural_col").style.display = "block"
    }
}
</script>
